data.description: Welcome to your oasis! Dive into luxury living with your very own saltwater inground pool, perfect for those sunny days of relaxation and fun! Step out onto the massive screened porch for the ultimate relaxation! Brand new roof, installed in 2022, ensuring peace of mind for years to come! Inside, you'll find hardwood floors that lead you to a cozy living room featuring an upgraded ceiling fan and a warm fireplace, creating the ideal ambiance for gatherings with loved ones! The kitchen has a breakfast bar, dishwasher, range, built-in microwave, refrigerator and a pantry for all your culinary needs! Start your day in the bright breakfast room illuminated by a charming light fixture! The owners suite features a tray ceiling, upgraded ceiling fan, a spacious walk-in closet and a bathroom with a double sink vanity, complete with awesome faucets, a soaking tub and a shower! Two additional bedrooms await, each adorned with ceiling fans for comfort! The guest bathroom shines with a stylish mirror and upgraded faucet! The laundry room, equipped with ceramic tile, makes chores a breeze! Enjoy a large fenced backyard, a private retreat for outdoor activities and gatherings! Additional features include two car garage, full sprinkler system maintaining your lush landscape, a hot water heater that is just one year new, ensuring endless comfort! This home is a true gem! Come and experience the epitome of modern living in this exceptional property!
